title: Area volleyball Super Ten
text:
October 14, 2015 | 11:58 am 
The area Super Ten volleyball teams, through matches played Tuesday, Oct. 13: 
1. WEST DELAWARE (38-2 overall, 7-0 Wamac East) 
2. CEDAR RAPIDS PRAIRIE (24-5 overall, 4-1 MVC Mississippi) 
3. CEDAR RAPIDS KENNEDY (22-8 overall, 6-0 MVC Valley) 
4. LINN-MAR (23-6 overall, 4-2 MVC Valley) 
5. CENTER POINT-URBANA (25-5 overall, 6-1 Wamac West) 
6. WEST BRANCH (30-4 overall, 6-0 River Valley South) 
7. IOWA CITY WEST (21-10 overall, 3-3 MVC Valley) 
8. MARION (23-7 overall, 7-0 Wamac West) 
9. WEST LIBERTY (29-4 overall, 5-1 River Valley South) 
10. IOWA CITY HIGH (13-12 overall, 5-1 MVC Mississippi) 
Area rankings by class: 
Class 5A — 1. C.R. Prairie (24-5), 2. C.R. Kennedy (22-8), 3. Linn-Mar (23-6), 4. Iowa City West (21-10), 5. Iowa City High (13-12). 
Class 4A — 1. West Delaware (38-2), 2. Marion (23-7), 3. Western Dubuque (17-11), 4. Independence (18-11), 5. Clear Creek Amana (17-12). 
Class 3A — 1. Center Point-Urbana (25-5), 2. West Liberty (29-4), 3. Mount Vernon (19-11), 4. Union (19-12), 5. Cascade (17-13). 
Class 2A — 1. West Branch (30-4), 2. Starmont (25-8), 3. Tipton (21-11), 4. North Cedar (26-9), 5. Jesup (15-15). 
Class 1A — 1. Springville (23-7), 2. Turkey Valley (17-5), 3. Iowa Valley (21-8), 4. Montezuma (18-5), 5. Lone Tree (15-10).
